63
00:04:47,667 --> 00:04:49,166
- Tak. - Sudah tentu saya suka...

64
00:04:49,167 --> 00:04:51,392
...Na Ji Na Ji Na yang berumur 29 tahun juga.

65
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:55,036
- Saya pun sayangkan awak, Tak. - Hei, tumpahlah.

66
00:04:55,037 --> 00:04:56,332
Tak.

67
00:04:57,776 --> 00:04:59,231
Bila awak nak ke hospital?

68
00:05:04,917 --> 00:05:06,445
Mak cik saya tak beritahu awak?

69
