143
00:10:13,157 --> 00:10:15,125
Bahagian di mana pelajar makan tteokbokki? Bahagian ini?

144
00:10:15,126 --> 00:10:17,556
Itu tak masuk akal.

145
00:10:17,557 --> 00:10:20,395
