184
00:12:06,197 --> 00:12:07,591
Dia takkan dengar cakap sesiapa.

185
00:12:09,707 --> 00:12:10,836
Kenapa kamu semua berkumpul?

186
00:12:10,837 --> 00:12:12,576
Kenapa awak lambat sangat, En. Cha?

187
00:12:12,577 --> 00:12:14,172
