203
00:12:46,177 --> 00:12:47,302
Hei!

204
00:12:47,537 --> 00:12:48,642
Lepaskan saya.

205
00:12:48,746 --> 00:12:50,601
- Bertenang. - Turun dari meja.

206
00:12:55,016 --> 00:12:56,111
