207
00:12:56,486 --> 00:12:58,412
Ini semua disebabkan awak.

208
00:13:06,527 --> 00:13:08,762
Anggap saja awak bertuah.

209
00:13:09,697 --> 00:13:11,561
Tak guna.

210
00:13:11,866 --> 00:13:13,836
Akhirnya saya dah faham.

211
00:13:13,837 --> 00:13:16,861
Patutlah semua novel awak akhirnya gagal.

212
