223
00:13:48,667 --> 00:13:50,061
Pihak yang menang.

224
00:13:52,236 --> 00:13:53,236
Maafkan saya.

225
00:13:53,237 --> 00:13:55,201
Saya tak boleh kawal kemarahan kalau jumpa lelaki macam dia.

226
00:13:56,476 --> 00:13:58,816
